Datasource.Parameter: (select geometry, type, round(st_area(geometry)) as area from osm_landusages order by area desc) as landusages
( SELECT geometry, type, name FROM osm_waterways WHERE type IN ('canal', 'river', 'stream') AND name IS NOT NULL) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type, name, ref, oneway, CHAR_LENGTH(ref) AS reflen FROM osm_motorways WHERE type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') AND (name IS NOT NULL OR ref IS NOT NULL)) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type, name, oneway FROM osm_mainroads WHERE name IS NOT NULL OR oneway <> 0) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type, name, oneway FROM osm_minorroads WHERE name IS NOT NULL OR oneway <> 0) AS data
